---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Pat Keenan"
  description="Software engineer. A bit about me, what I work on, and this site."
>
  <article class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      I'm Pat Keenan, a software engineer focused on building reliable, well-crafted software.
      This site is where I write about what I'm learning, tools I like, and projects I work on.
    </p>

    <h2>What I Work On</h2>
    <p>
      I spend most of my time writing TypeScript and working across the full web stack. I'm particularly
      interested in developer tooling, static site generation, and the craft of writing maintainable code.
    </p>

    <h2>This Site</h2>
    <p>
      Styled with <a href="https://tailwindcss.com">Tailwind CSS</a> and deployed on <a href="https://vercel.com">Vercel</a>.
      Posts are plain Markdown files.
      No CMS, no database — just files in a git repository.
    </p>
    <p>
      Source is on <a href="https://github.com">GitHub</a> if you're curious.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      You can find me on <a href="https://github.com">GitHub</a>.
      For anything else, reach out by email.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
